name: 22 CLOSE UP TAKEOFFS AND LANDINGS! Montreal (YUL) Airport Runway 24L/24R
description:
The third and final installment of YUL footage from my trip there back in August - a collection of miscellaneous landings and takeoffs on the 24s!

With thanks to  @MarkBrandonAviation
